<A NAME="Toolbar"><H2>Using the Toolbar</H2></A>
<P>The word processor toolbar contains several icons you can click on to access these options:

<UL>
<TABLE BORDER = 0><TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vprnt"><TD><B>Printer</B> allows you to configure the NC for the attached printer.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vregi"><TD><B>Region</B> allows you to set localized aspects of the NC.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmode"><TD><B>Modem</B> allows you to configure the NC for the phone system it uses.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vmoni"><TD><B>Monitor</B> allows you to configure the NC for the attached monitor.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vvers"><TD><B>Version</B> displays the software version information.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vhelp"><TD><B>Help</B> displays the help screen.<TR><TD>
<IMG WIDTH=25 HEIGHT=25 SRC="icontype:nc_vclos"><TD><B>Close</B> quits the administration application.<TR><TD>
</TABLE>
</UL>

